title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 14 2022
description:
Ukrainian president Zelensky posts on Facebook that Russia will invade on Wednesday. Clay and Buck listen in to a Pentagon press conference on Ukraine. Buck uses his CIA background to analyze the Ukraine situation. U.S. calls for destruction of sensitive documents in Kiev embassy. Will Putin invasion of Ukraine during Beijing Olympics embolden China to take Taiwan? Will Trudeau invoke martial law to crack down on trucker protest?
